    "text": "You can run and dive \nat enemies with a slide\nattack. To do this \nmove in Standard Mode,\nrun and then press .\nTo jump out of the \nslide and land back on \nyour feet, press either\n or .\n\nOnly mustached players\ncan pull this move off.\nDon't even think of \ntrying it if you don't\nhave a mustache!"
