    "text": "Pssst! The Boos are \nsuper shy. If you look\nthem in the eyes, they\nfade away.\nThey reappear when \nyou turn your back, \nso don't let them \nsneak up on you!\nIt's no use trying to \nhit them when they're \nfading away. \n\nInstead, sneak up\nfrom behind and punch\nthem.\n\nYou can't swallow \nBoos, so this is where \nyou'll need a mustached\nhero to save the day. "
